<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Hot Headz Southern Foods</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Southern comfort food in DeRidder, Louisiana." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f0f10;
      --bg-soft: #171719;
      --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --text: #f8f2e8;
      --muted: #d6c7b0;
      --gold: #f0b24b;
      --red: #d54b2f;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      --radius: 24px;
      --max: 1180px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(213,75,47,0.22), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(240,178,75,0.16), transparent 22%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #111214 0%, #0d0d0f 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }

    .container { width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 32px)); margin: 0 auto; }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 30;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      background: rgba(10,10,11,0.72);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      min-height: 72px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .brand-badge {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--red));
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: #111;
      font-weight: 900;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--muted);
      transition: 180ms ease;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }

    .cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 13px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform 180ms ease, opacity 180ms ease, background 180ms ease;
    }

    .cta:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .cta-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #ffcf7b);
      color: #1a1206;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .cta-secondary {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 72px 0 44px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .panel {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), rgba(255,255,255,0.04));
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      padding: 44px;
      position: relative;
      min-height: 520px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      width: fit-content;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(240,178,75,0.12);
      color: #ffd993;
      border: 1px solid rgba(240,178,75,0.22);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.6rem);
      line-height: 0.96;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .hero-copy p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 58ch;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 26px;
    }

    .hero-meta {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 34px;
    }

    .meta-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.045);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .meta-card span {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .meta-card strong {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .hero-gallery {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: 1.3fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
      min-height: 520px;
    }

    .gallery-main,
    .gallery-stack > div {
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 22px;
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 180px;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .gallery-main::after,
    .gallery-stack > div::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.45));
    }

    .gallery-stack {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    section {
      padding: 28px 0;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: end;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .section-head h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .section-head p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 60ch;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .cards-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .feature-card,
    .menu-card,
    .info-card,
    .delivery-card {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), rgba(255,255,255,0.04));
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .feature-card h3,
    .menu-card h3,
    .info-card h3,
    .delivery-card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .feature-card p,
    .menu-card p,
    .info-card p,
    .delivery-card p,
    .menu-card li,
    .hours li {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .feature-icon {
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      background: rgba(240,178,75,0.14);
      color: #ffd993;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .menu-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .menu-card ul,
    .hours {
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
    }

    .banner {
      padding: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .banner-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(213,75,47,0.18), rgba(240,178,75,0.18));
    }

    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .info-card a { color: #ffd993; }

    footer {
      padding: 28px 0 50px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .footer-wrap {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding-top: 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .info-grid,
      .cards-3,
      .menu-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-copy { min-height: auto; }
      .hero-gallery { min-height: auto; }
      .hero-meta { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .banner-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .nav { padding: 12px 0; align-items: start; flex-direction: column; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 620px) {
      .hero-copy { padding: 28px; }
      h1 { font-size: 2.6rem; }
      .section-head { align-items: start; flex-direction: column; }
      .gallery-stack { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="container nav">
      <a class="brand" href="#home" aria-label="Hot Headz Southern Foods home">
        <div class="brand-badge">HH</div>
        <div>
          <div>Hot Headz</div>
          <small style="color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600;">Southern Foods</small>
        </div>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Primary navigation">
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#menu">Menu</a>
        <a href="#delivery">Delivery</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <a class="cta cta-primary" href="tel:+13372211035">Call to Order</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="home">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="panel hero-copy">
          <div class="eyebrow">Fresh daily • Southern comfort food</div>
          <h1>Hot Headz<br />Southern Foods</h1>
          <p>
            A polished, original GitHub Pages landing page inspired by the feel of a warm Southern cafeteria:
            bold headline, quick actions, clear hours, menu sections, and local-first contact details.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="cta cta-primary" href="#menu">View Menu</a>
            <a class="cta cta-secondary" href="#contact">Find Us</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-meta">
            <div class="meta-card">
              <span>Location</span>
              <strong>DeRidder, Louisiana</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-card">
              <span>Service</span>
              <strong>Dine-In • Carry-Out • Delivery</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-card">
              <span>Phone</span>
              <strong>(337) 221-1035</strong>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel hero-gallery" aria-label="Food gallery preview">
          <div class="gallery-main" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504674900247-0877df9cc836?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80');"></div>
          <div class="gallery-stack">
            <div style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544025162-d76694265947?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80');"></div>
            <div style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1525351484163-7529414344d8?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80');"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Why people stop in</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Designed for a restaurant homepage that needs to convert fast: clear information, strong calls to action, and a cozy visual identity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cards-3">
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">☀️</div>
            <h3>Breakfast & lunch focus</h3>
            <p>Built around the rhythm of a local café with space for daily specials, plate lunches, and quick family-style ordering.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🍗</div>
            <h3>Comfort food feel</h3>
            <p>Warm gradients, bold typography, and roomy cards give the page a fresh but down-home Southern look.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">📍</div>
            <h3>Easy to contact</h3>
            <p>Sticky navigation, tap-to-call, and visible location details keep the page useful on both desktop and mobile.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="menu">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Menu sections</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Swap these sample items with your current menu or wire this page to a Google Doc, PDF, or online ordering platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-grid">
          <article class="menu-card">
            <h3>Breakfast plates</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Biscuits and gravy</li>
              <li>Egg plates with bacon or sausage</li>
              <li>Grits, toast, hash browns</li>
              <li>Breakfast sandwiches</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="menu-card">
            <h3>Lunch favorites</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Fried chicken and sides</li>
              <li>Smothered meats and rice</li>
              <li>Daily vegetables</li>
              <li>Rotating Southern specials</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="menu-card">
            <h3>Extras</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Salad bar</li>
              <li>Desserts</li>
              <li>Tea, soft drinks, coffee</li>
              <li>Family-size add-ons</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="menu-card">
            <h3>Ordering options</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Dine-in</li>
              <li>Carry-out</li>
              <li>Large-order delivery</li>
              <li>Phone orders</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="delivery">
      <div class="container panel banner">
        <div class="banner-inner">
          <div>
            <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px;">Delivery for larger orders</h2>
            <p style="margin:0; color: var(--muted);">Use this area for delivery rules, catering notes, or a third-party ordering button.</p>
          </div>
          <a class="cta cta-primary" href="tel:+13372211035">Order by Phone</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
      <div class="container info-grid">
        <article class="info-card">
          <h3>About the brand</h3>
          <p>
            This layout is intentionally original rather than a pixel-for-pixel copy. It keeps the same broad restaurant-site structure—hero, menu, delivery, hours, contact, and footer—while avoiding a direct clone.
          </p>
          <p>
            For an exact business-ready launch, replace the sample gallery with your own food photos and update every section to match your branding.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="info-card" id="contact">
          <h3>Hours & contact</h3>
          <ul class="hours">
            <li>Mon–Fri: 5:30 AM – 2:00 PM</li>
            <li>Saturday: 6:00 AM – 2:00 PM</li>
            <li>Sunday: 7:00 AM – 3:00 PM</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+13372211035">(337) 221-1035</a></p>
          <p><strong>Address:</strong> 2741 US-190, DeRidder, LA 70634</p>
          <p><strong>Maps:</strong> <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=2741+US-190+DeRidder+LA+70634" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Open directions</a></p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container footer-wrap">
      <div>© <span id="year"></span> Hot Headz Southern Foods</div>
      <div>Built as a static GitHub Pages site</div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
